AttributeList.Text:
Control addon that can be activated at the early stage of commisioning multiple machines at the same time to control X and Y axis jogging without PC.
To activate control buttons: enable function blocks in FTON and type with jog buttons combination: Z1 up, Z2 down, Z2 up, Z1 down, Z1 up, Z2 down, Z2 up, Z1 down,
Deactivate: hold all 4 buttons at the same time

Details to start the logging process: 1) Activate web server 2) Set variables to log by assigning them to DataLogging block inputs 3) Create logging file in the FTON 4) Start logging in the FTON 5) Download the file via web server
There is a limited amount of data that can be written due to limited memory capacity. The file will be overwritten after certain amount of records. It is possible to create a new file based on amount of records, should be developed in the future.
